snippet.title: SINNER: Sacrifice for Redemption - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Embark on a journey of self-discover in SINNER: Sacrifice for Redemption as you guide Adam on a path to atone for his sins. Do battle with avatars of Adam’s Sin in eight furious boss battles. Weaken yourself as you sacrifice you strength, skill, and supplies, to prove your worth and redeem your soul.

Available 10/18 on Nintendo Switch! https://goo.gl/ySNuxp

#NintendoSwitch #SinnerSacrificeForRedemption
